flowRoot.flowPara: - The terrain borders need to be in a group. The top right corner of the group specifies where the border will be in the sprite. So don't draw anything outside of the yellow rectangles.
- The ID of the group must be set to group1_group2_left, group1_group2_center, or group1_group2_right. With Inkscape, use Object > Object Properties from the menu to set it.
- Anything else doesn't matter, but keeping the file clean will improve rendering time.
